---
import Icon from './Icon.astro';
// Footer component
---

<footer class="bg-gray-800 text-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Main Footer Content -->
    <div class="py-12 lg:py-16">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <!-- Brand Column -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-2">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
            <div class="text-3xl mr-3">⚖️</div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">PesoTracker</h3>
          </div>
          
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
            La aplicación más completa para gestionar tu peso con tecnología de vanguardia. 
            Desarrollada para macOS con SwiftUI y cariño.
          </p>
          
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
            <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-gray-700 text-green-400 text-sm rounded-full border border-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-600 transition-colors duration-200">macOS Nativo</span>
            <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-gray-700 text-green-400 text-sm rounded-full border border-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-600 transition-colors duration-200">SwiftUI</span>
            <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-gray-700 text-green-400 text-sm rounded-full border border-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-600 transition-colors duration-200">Open Source</span>
            <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-gray-700 text-green-400 text-sm rounded-full border border-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-600 transition-colors duration-200">Gratuito</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Links Column -->
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-6">Enlaces</h4>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div>
              <a 
                href="https://github.com/StevenACZ/peso-tracker/releases/tag/v1.2.3" 
                target="_blank" 
                rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer"
                class="text-gray-300 hover:text-green-400 transition-colors duration-200 flex items-center"
              >
                <Icon name="download" size="sm" class="mr-2" />
                Descargar App
              </a>
            </div>
            <div>
              <a 
                href="https://github.com/StevenACZ/peso-tracker" 
                target="_blank" 
                rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer"
                class="text-gray-300 hover:text-green-400 transition-colors duration-200 flex items-center"
              >
                <Icon name="code" size="sm" class="mr-2" />
                Código Fuente
              </a>
            </div>
            <div>
              <a 
                href="https://github.com/StevenACZ/peso-tracker/releases" 
                target="_blank" 
                rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer"
                class="text-gray-300 hover:text-green-400 transition-colors duration-200 flex items-center"
              >
                <Icon name="refresh" size="sm" class="mr-2" />
                Todas las Versiones
              </a>
            </div>
            <div>
              <a 
                href="https://github.com/StevenACZ/peso-tracker/issues" 
                target="_blank" 
                rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer"
                class="text-gray-300 hover:text-green-400 transition-colors duration-200 flex items-center"
              >
                <Icon name="info" size="sm" class="mr-2" />
                Soporte
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Developer Column -->
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-6">Desarrollador</h4>
          
          <div class="mb-6">
            <div class="flex items-start mb-4 space-x-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500 to-emerald-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-lg flex-shrink-0">
                SA
              </div>
              <div class="flex-1">
                <h5 class="text-gray-100 font-semibold text-base leading-none my-0">Steven ACZ</h5>
                <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm leading-none my-0 mt-2">Full Stack Developer</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Desarrollador apasionado por crear aplicaciones nativas de alta calidad para macOS.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Social Links -->
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <div>
              <a 
                href="https://linkedin.com/in/stevenacz" 
                target="_blank" 
                rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer"
                class="inline-flex items-center text-gray-300 hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors duration-200"
              >
                <Icon name="linkedin" size="sm" class="mr-2" />
                LinkedIn
              </a>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <a 
                href="https://github.com/StevenACZ" 
                target="_blank" 
                rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer"
                class="inline-flex items-center text-gray-300 hover:text-gray-100 transition-colors duration-200"
              >
                <Icon name="github" size="sm" class="mr-2" />
                GitHub
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bottom Bar -->
    <div class="border-t border-gray-700 py-8">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4">
        <div class="text-gray-300 text-sm mb-4 md:mb-0 text-center">
          <p>© 2025 Steven ACZ. Desarrollado con SwiftUI y cariño <span aria-label="corazón">❤️</span></p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center md:justify-end gap-x-4 gap-y-2 text-sm text-gray-300">
          <span class="flex items-center">
            <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full mr-2 animate-pulse"></div>
            v1.2.3 Disponible
          </span>
          <span class="text-gray-400 hidden sm:inline">|</span>
          <span>macOS 15.5+</span>
          <span class="text-gray-400 hidden sm:inline">|</span>
          <span>Open Source</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>